headline: Morgan Stanley Expansion Capital Makes $20 Million Investment in NovoPayment
summary: NEW YORK, November 12, 2024--Investment funds managed by Morgan Stanley Expansion Capital announced today an investment of $20 million in NovoPayment, a leading financial and payment infrastructure service provider specializing in delivering digital banking, payments and card solutions.
